sequenceDiagram
    participant Runner as DSP Pipeline Runner
    participant APIServer as DSP API Server
    participant UI as DSP UI
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP

    Note over Runner, DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    Runner->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifacts + events)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Configurable TLS | Configurable mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata records<br/>DB Protocol | Configurable TLS | Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Acknowledgement
    MLMD-->>Runner: PutExecutionResponse

    Runner->>MLMD: PutArtifacts<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Configurable TLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts<br/>DB Protocol | Configurable TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Acknowledgement
    MLMD-->>Runner: PutArtifactsResponse

    Runner->>MLMD: PutEvents (lineage)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Configurable TLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT events<br/>DB Protocol | Configurable TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Acknowledgement
    MLMD-->>Runner: PutEventsResponse

    Note over UI, DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Metadata Query / Lineage Retrieval

    UI->>APIServer: Request artifact lineage
    APIServer->>MLMD: GetLineageGraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Configurable TLS | Configurable mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT lineage data<br/>DB Protocol | Configurable TLS | Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set
    MLMD-->>APIServer: GetLineageGraphResponse
    APIServer-->>UI: Lineage visualization data

    APIServer->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Configurable TLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts by context<br/>DB Protocol | Configurable TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set
    MLMD-->>APIServer: GetArtifactsByContextResponse
